{#
  outreach_email.jinja2 — First-touch cold email template
  Tenacious Consulting & Outsourcing SDR Agent

  Required variables:
    company_name        (str)  — prospect company name
    contact_first_name  (str)  — prospect's first name
    segment             (int)  — ICP segment 1–4
    signal_opening      (str)  — pre-computed signal statement at correct register
                                 (produced by signal_honesty.get_register())
    bridge              (str)  — 1–2 sentences connecting the signal to a common pattern
                                 (segment-specific, generated by agent)
    case_study_line     (str|None) — one redacted outcome line, optional
    qualification_ask   (str)  — single low-commitment qualifying question
    sender_name         (str)  — SDR / account executive name shown in signature

  Output:
    Subject line (6 words max, no punctuation)
    Plain-text body (≤ 120 words)

  Guardrail notes:
    - signal_opening must carry the correct assert/hedge/ask register BEFORE this template
      is rendered — the template does not re-check register logic.
    - tone_checker.enforce() must be called on the rendered output before send.
    - Do not add punctuation to the subject line.
#}

{# ── Subject line ── #}
{% if segment == 1 %}
Subject: Engineering squad for post-funding velocity {{ company_name }}
{% elif segment == 2 %}
Subject: Delivery capacity after the reorg {{ company_name }}
{% elif segment == 3 %}
Subject: Squad support for your first 90 days
{% elif segment == 4 %}
Subject: Closing the capability gap at {{ company_name }}
{% else %}
Subject: Engineering capacity for {{ company_name }}
{% endif %}

{# ── Body ── #}
{{ contact_first_name }},

{{ signal_opening }}

{% if segment == 1 %}
{{ bridge }}
Post-funding engineering backlogs tend to outpace hiring timelines. We embed dedicated squads in 2–3 weeks with no permanent headcount added.
{% elif segment == 2 %}
{{ bridge }}
When headcount reductions leave a delivery gap, a time-boxed squad engagement keeps commitments on track without reversing the cost structure you just built.
{% elif segment == 3 %}
{{ bridge }}
New engineering leaders often need immediate capacity for a priority initiative before the org is fully built out. We can run alongside your team for a scoped project.
{% elif segment == 4 %}
{{ bridge }}
Specialized capability gaps are slow to close through hiring alone. Our bench has engineers in that space available now.
{% else %}
{{ bridge }}
{% endif %}

{% if case_study_line %}
For context: {{ case_study_line }}

{% endif %}
{{ qualification_ask }}

{{ sender_name }}
Tenacious Consulting & Outsourcing
